itl.enabler.api.types

Enum DataType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<DataType>
      • itl.enabler.api.types.DataType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<DataType>

    public enum DataType
extends java.lang.Enum<DataType>
    Data type to inform the Enabler of a database update using the Forecourt.notifyChange(ActionType, DataType, int) method

    You will need to read the Enabler Database Dictionary to fully understand the meaning of these values.

      • TANK_LEVEL_CHANGED

        public static final DataType TANK_LEVEL_CHANGED
        Used when the tank level fields have been updated in the tank table row to update the tank object in memory. This can be used to enter tank level readings from an external tank gauge which is not connected to the system.

        DataID = Tank Id of tank to read levels
